
# d750-settings.md

[D750 Settings](https://photographylife.com/recommended-nikon-d750-settings)

Back focus button
- AE/AF Lock - AF-on 
- Sub Selector Dial Centre - AF Area Mode + AF on

Metering
- Single point
- Matrix

AF Mode
- AF-C - Continuous

ISO Auto 100-3200

Store Points in Orientation
- a8 in Custom settings menu

set up the center OK button on the multi-selector to zoom in and out to a set magnification level when reviewing images with a single press of the button!